{"tid":870544,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【四大皆空】常霖法師已出家仲去囡囡婚禮？廖安麗稱唔去個女嬲一世","createTime":"2018-10-21T08:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:23:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7907d1231ca2d18f31bc216d0a931c05dc2fd722","tid":870544,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"本月13號，廖安麗同前夫常霖法師葉青霖嘅大女喺澳洲出嫁，身為父母嘅當然有到場見住囡囡成為人妻，翌日常霖法師更喺社交網站寄語女兒，分享夫妻相處之道，謂「執子之手，與子偕老，重點在過程，而不在結果。」<br />\n不過，有網民質疑已經出家嘅常霖法師咁做其實已經犯戒，認為出家人就應該四大皆空，如果唔割愛辭親，出家就變得無意義。<br />\n對此廖安麗接受周刊訪問表示咁做一啲都唔出奇，佢話常霖法師平時經常都會搞活動弘法，仲話好多人以為出家即係喺深山修行，廖安麗表示平時跟常霖法師學攝影嘅徒弟結婚的話法師亦都會出席，更何況如果唔到場，囡囡分分鐘嬲爸爸一世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181020/large/1540025398_9b24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181020%2Flarge%2F1540025398_9b24.jpg&h=26bf2aa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9f74eadba5b5920326f7a90785a7295fe6b2027","tid":870544,"uid":141782,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"拋妻棄女唔係最大嘅孽咩<br />\n仲修乜鬼行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13655758e4cf3ab05a6d91e6e58a7ed3f747a4f7","tid":870544,"uid":14497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"平時係深山食師姑"},{"pid":"aa92e97d50fc6625d0839577e9f62c606b3a42ca","tid":870544,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9f74eadba5b5920326f7a90785a7295fe6b2027","tid":870544,"uid":141782,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"拋妻棄女唔係最大嘅孽咩<br />\n仲修乜鬼行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"不是孽吧？"},{"pid":"48a8b7a3d1d8bf4d249870fb38382046ce23f268","tid":870544,"uid":26329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"aa92e97d50fc6625d0839577e9f62c606b3a42ca","tid":870544,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9f74eadba5b5920326f7a90785a7295fe6b2027","tid":870544,"uid":141782,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"拋妻棄女唔係最大嘅孽咩<br />\n仲修乜鬼行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"不是孽吧？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"出家學道，成道正覺 回去對家人說法先係最大既功德<br />\n但出家就唔應該再涉及係家庭入面<br />\n例如係佛陀時期某某尊者既老婆仔女黎搵佢叫佢番屋企，該位尊者另開一面，不作回應"},{"pid":"37af13f8e0ae6b621a08ea3c6138fb0f2c6f6cad","tid":870544,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"何謂出家<br />\n出家後家人唔再係家人<br />\n點化個女戒嗔戒恨得唔得?"},{"pid":"a00468c89d8e50e6e83d2a7deb4f12de1a13ae81","tid":870544,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37af13f8e0ae6b621a08ea3c6138fb0f2c6f6cad","tid":870544,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"何謂出家<br />\n出家後家人唔再係家人<br />\n點化個女戒嗔戒恨得唔得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"眾生都係你家人"},{"pid":"1765089014870387363b20411c99e5152bdf9590","tid":870544,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13655758e4cf3ab05a6d91e6e58a7ed3f747a4f7","tid":870544,"uid":14497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"平時係深山食師姑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91a2198fb874a7c2c48ab7a1d5a865539534783","tid":870544,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:13:16.000Z","msg":"常人對佛教最大既誤會就係拜佛做和尚,根本上一開始就係反對崇拜偶像"},{"pid":"d39fb2a231e8f503a13b7927d3deb9add46bffd6","tid":870544,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"還俗啦你"},{"pid":"d8a90b8eb2b917f1ec146b55cc11ccd5